clicky-plus (1.1.3) una; urgency=low

  * Hardening: Fixed wipe-on-resize drawing persistence bug.
  * Hardening: Fixed GtkFileChooserButton GSettings binding crash.
  * Hardening: Improved Blur tool compatibility for non-Image surfaces.
  * Hardening: Fixed CLI mode argument parsing variables.
  * Packaging: Added missing python3-pil and ffmpeg dependencies.
  * Cleanup: Removed redundant scripts and build artifacts.

